OL,6,F"Toto was a great footballer, a
OL,7,Ftenacious symbol of will and
OL,8,Fredemption, he was able to thrill the
OL,9,FAzzurri fans because his football was
OL,10,Ffull of passion.
OL,12,F"And it was precisely this indomitable
OL,13,Fspirit that made him appreciated by
OL,14,Feveryone and will make him immortal."
OL,16,FHis family announced last week he had
OL,17,Fbeen admitted to hospital.
